Hello there,

Im using the function 'content_by_id' a lot but I reached my limit really quick.
We are using a lot of modules on one page where one or more calls are made.

```&lt;div class="wrapper"&gt;
  {% for spotlight in  module.spotlights %}
    {% set this_spotlight = content_by_id(spotlight.page) %}
    ....
  {% endfor %}
&lt;/div&gt;```
So my question is, is there a workaround to get more calls per page?
I already found content_by_ids for some modules, But I will still reach the max too quick
